leve.name: Fish Oils and Forgotten Spoils
leve.description: As House Dzemael toils to restore Falcon's Nest to its former glory, the carpenters employed seek to restore the villagers' own charred furnishings to their former glory. The house artisans are known for their obsession with detail, and consultations with surviving visitors tell of using grass carp oil as a veneer to glue pieces of wood together in their armoires. Mayhap you can gather some to aid the restoration efforts?
leve.client: Temple Knights Minister of Coin, Amianne Tristelle
